{
  "stem": "7873.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I always saw them walking in line with pieces of timber for the fire.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the evening, we stay in roll call.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had to have-- after roll call, we used to get a little bit of soup.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there's a person missing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We're standing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were standing for hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Finally decided, started to-- some-- that's what they did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it's already late at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we are standing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Dead or alive, they've got to have the person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Or the person could've got lost in the mud.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's how much mud we had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Or somebody threw him in the toilet, in the latrine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they're looking for the dead-- for the body.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Doesn't matter to them what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Otherwise, he says he's not going to sign the roll call.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the two guys-- they are paying attention to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're keeping it clean and everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had an idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a barrack just for dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't burn fast enough on the fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They kept them in stack on the-- hundreds of them stacked up until under the ceiling-- bodies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were two doors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you keep pushing them forward through the one door, forward.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went into that barrack.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They opened up one door, the back door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There is a guy already-- where, where the guy died-- or beaten to death, whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They undressed him naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they put with magic marker the number on his stomach.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was laying in the back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he called the roll call, so many live ones and one dead, or two dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're all-- as he goes into the dead house, he sees already all the dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He, he said, I didn't know what I'm looking for.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
